regen.absent_element: recording of the "unit unavailable" event triggered by a denied request
regen.new_specification: The system shall record each "unit unavailable" event triggered by a denied request from a thermostat.

regen.absent_element: Specification for recording the generated event
regen.new_specification: The system shall record each generated event of a denied request for future reference.

regen.absent_element: action of linking to previous related events
regen.new_specification: The system shall reference any prior events associated with the same thermostat or unit in the generated event.

label: This system event shall contain a designation of the heating or cooling unit that was not turned.
absence: the designation of the not turned unit should be contained in the event
